'''Complexity theory''' (or complexity science) is the study of [[complexity]] and of [[complex systems]]. It may also refer to: * [[Complexity theory and organizations]], the application of complexity theory to strategy * [[Complexity economics]], the application of complexity theory to economics * [[Complex adaptive system]], a special case of complex systems * [[Computational complexity theory]], a field in theoretical computer science and mathematics
